#### Description

Listen for paste events in the TipTap editor. When text is pasted, cross-reference it against copy records synced from the extension. If a matching copy record is found, prepare the paste data for RED attribution tagging.

#### Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Paste events in the TipTap editor are intercepted before content is inserted
- [ ] Clipboard text is extracted from the paste event
