#### Files to Create/Modify

- `packages/editor/src/attribution/paste-handler.ts` — (create) paste event interception and matching logic
- `packages/editor/src/attribution/copy-record-matcher.ts` — (create) search copy records for paste match
- `packages/editor/src/extensions/paste-plugin.ts` — (create) TipTap plugin for paste interception
- `packages/editor/src/components/Editor.tsx` — (modify) register paste plugin

#### Implementation Notes

Use TipTap's `addProseMirrorPlugins` to create a plugin that intercepts paste:

```typescript
import { Plugin, PluginKey } from '@tiptap/pm/state';

const pastePluginKey = new PluginKey('attribution-paste');

new Plugin({
  key: pastePluginKey,
  props: {
    handlePaste(view, event, slice) {
      const clipboardText = event.clipboardData?.getData('text/plain');
      if (!clipboardText) return false;
      // Match against copy records, then insert with attribution
      matchAndInsert(view, clipboardText, slice);
      return true; // we handle insertion
    },
  },
});
```

For matching: compare `clipboardText` against copy records. Use exact string match first, then fuzzy match (>95% similarity) for cases where whitespace/formatting differs slightly.

