#### Description

When a paste matches a copy record (or AI pool entry via fallback), insert the text into the editor with the `AttributionMark` set to RED, including source metadata and original paste content.

#### Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Matched pastes are inserted with `AttributionMark` color='red'
- [ ] Mark attributes include: paste_event_id, original_paste_content, confidence, created_at
- [ ] The original paste content is stored verbatim for later edit-distance comparison
- [ ] Non-AI pastes (no match) are inserted with `AttributionMark` color='green'
